{
 "name": "RPlog_Post-Surgery",
 "title": "Post-Surgery",
 "summary": "Aboard the shuttle Black Ice, the anxious Mailyn Raines keeps vigil over the unconscious Simon Sezirok, the Selas, kept alive after delicate surgery by the healer Satine. The pilot Kyyel Marrak arrives, and he and Mailyn talk in hushed tones about her reasons for fighting to give Simon a chance at redemption, the intelligence Kyyel seeks about Karrde's supposed plans against the Jedi, and the tangled loyalties between them. When Simon finally stirs and groggily addresses Mailyn with the intimate Telgossian name 'Beledonna,' recalling a vision of her bathed in light as he gave up his fight, the moment grows painfully tender and awkward. Overwhelmed and disappointed by the devotion she sees misplaced, Mailyn excuses herself to find Satine as Kyyel quietly departs, leaving Simon to slip back into drugged sleep.",
